Description

Card
Class that implements a card object, it assumes that: H - hearts (copas) D - diamonds (oiros) S - spades (espadas) C - clubs (paus) Ace --> 1 Numbers: 2 to 9 Number 10 --> T Jack --> 11 Queen --> 12 King --> 13

This class is used as a helper to evaluate and analyze the hand.
